  <entry>
    <title>我的第一篇blog 搭建GitHub+hexo的blog</title>
    <link href="http://super1010.github.io/archives/4d5d007a.html"/>
    <id>http://super1010.github.io/archives/4d5d007a.html</id>
    <published>2020-03-28T14:47:24.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-04-12T15:09:51.686Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>各类系统 演示步骤可参阅<br><a href="https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Yb411a7ty?t=1551" target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Yb411a7ty?t=1551</a><br>所遇问题见弹幕<br>本文基于Windows10</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="第一章-Windows下搭建环境"><a href="#第一章-Windows下搭建环境" class="headerlink" title="第一章 Windows下搭建环境"></a>第一章 Windows下搭建环境</h2><p>下载并安装 node.js和git<br><a href="https://nodejs.org/en/" target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">https://nodejs.org/en/</a><br><a href="https://git-scm.com/downloads" target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">https://git-scm.com/downloads</a></p><hr><h2 id="第二章-开始写博文"><a href="#第二章-开始写博文" class="headerlink" title="第二章 开始写博文"></a>第二章 开始写博文</h2><p>在cmd命令行下cd进入blog目录</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo n <span class="string">"标题"</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>创建了一个新标题</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> <span class="built_in">source</span>/_posts/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>进入子目录</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ notepad 标题</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>打开刚才标题下的博文</p><p>写完后保存 退出</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> ../..</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>退回到blog</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">$ hexo g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>生成博客</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>重新启动<br>关闭</p><hr><h2 id="第三章-安装插件"><a href="#第三章-安装插件" class="headerlink" title="第三章 安装插件"></a>第三章 安装插件</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>dir 命令查看文件夹下文件 相当于ls</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ notepad _config.yml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p> 在最下端贴上地址按教程修改</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>部署到远端</p><hr><h2 id="第四章-下载与设置theme"><a href="#第四章-下载与设置theme" class="headerlink" title="第四章 下载与设置theme"></a>第四章 下载与设置theme</h2><p>可选择各种主题<br><a href="https://hexo.io/themes/" target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">https://hexo.io/themes/</a><br>我选择了yilia</p><p>下载与安装yilia<br><a href="https://github.com/litten/hexo-theme-yilia" target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">https://github.com/litten/hexo-theme-yilia</a></p><p>进阶修改yilia<br><a href="https://tding.top/archives/9a232bbe.html" target="_blank" rel="external nofollow noopener noreferrer">https://tding.top/archives/9a232bbe.html</a></p><p>在md文章中需要截断的地方添加</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ &lt;!-- more --&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>要添加多个标签，tags后面这样写就行了</p><p>tags: [标签1,标签2,标签3]</p>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;各类系统 演示步骤可参阅&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Yb411a7ty?t=1551&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;external nofollow noopener noreferrer&quot;&gt;https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1Yb411a7ty?t=1551&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;所遇问题见弹幕&lt;br&gt;本文基于Windows10&lt;/p&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
    
    
